    <item>
      <title>中国与我们一起脱身</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-06/china-takes-gloves-off-in-trade-war-with-us-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从4月10日开始，中国将对美国的所有进口征收34％的关税。它与特朗普所谓的中国产品所谓的相互关税相匹配。彭博的斯蒂芬·恩格尔（Stephen Engle）来自香港。 （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-06/china-takes-gloves-off-in-trade-war-with-us-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 22:10:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国股票期货在特朗普团队挖掘关税的情况下跌跌撞撞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/us-stock-futures-tumble-with-trump-team-digging-in-on-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国股票期货暴跌，这使S＆amp; P 500在熊市的范围内走上了正轨，因为特朗普政府挖掘贸易战争经济学家警告说，将使世界上最大的经济体陷入衰退。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/us-stock-futures-tumble-with-trump-team-digging-in-on-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 22:04:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>石油延伸时，沙特阿拉伯跌幅和关税风险越来越低落</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-7</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在沙特阿拉伯将其旗舰原油价格削减了两年多以来，石油在本周的开放式上倒下了，而不断升级的贸易战激发了人们对全球衰退和能源需求较弱的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-7</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 22:03:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>El-Erian说，市场抛售一直是不利的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-06/market-selloff-has-been-indiscriminate-el-erian-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[剑桥皇后学院校长兼彭博舆论专栏作家穆罕默德·埃里安（Mohamed El-Erian）表示，这种市场抛售是不加区分的。他谈到了对未来一周的特别“彭博监视”的期望。他的意见是他自己的。 （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-06/market-selloff-has-been-indiscriminate-el-erian-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 21:43:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>铜的公牛奔跑变成了溃败，关税的现实咬合</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/copper-s-bull-run-turns-into-a-rout-as-reality-of-tariffs-bites</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两周前，交易员警告说，威胁我们对金属的关税会挤压全球供应，铜价飙升。现在，随着唐纳德·特朗普总统的更广泛的贸易战争使需求的前景更加重要，铜牛正面临有史以来最糟糕的抛售之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/copper-s-bull-run-turns-into-a-rout-as-reality-of-tariffs-bites</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 21:31:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普：关税会留在这里</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-06/trump-tariffs-are-here-to-stay-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统并没有为他们创造的市场动荡而道歉。彭博社的泰勒·肯德尔（Tyler Kendall）报道了白宫。 （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-06/trump-tariffs-are-here-to-stay-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 21:30:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国放松了电动汽车的销售任务，在狂热者对特朗普关税的回应中</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/uk-eases-ev-sales-mandate-in-starmer-response-to-trump-s-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理凯尔·斯塔默（Keir Starmer）正在采取第一步，通过放大政府的电动汽车销售任务来帮助英国企业承受美国关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/uk-eases-ev-sales-mandate-in-starmer-response-to-trump-s-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 21:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元，瑞士法郎拉力赛，当交易者寻求避风税违背的避风港</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/yen-swiss-franc-rally-as-traders-seek-havens-on-tariff-defiance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日元和瑞士法郎周一加强了周一，因为交易员在美国官员表示违反贸易关税后寻求避风港，并表示将延长有关降低关税的谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/yen-swiss-franc-rally-as-traders-seek-havens-on-tariff-defiance</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 21:27:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的关税“死亡表”使华尔街面临严酷的现实</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/trump-tariff-chart-how-stock-market-crash-hits-wall-street-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国投资者班级＆Mdash; 拥有几乎所有股票的前10％; 在唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的贸易攻势时代，很快就会遵守其新的，艰巨的地位。从企业高管将其股票期权计算到亿万富翁对冲基金大亨以及介于两者之间的每个人，现在只是附带损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/trump-tariff-chart-how-stock-market-crash-hits-wall-street-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 21:01:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普团队拒绝市场恐惧，表现出对关税的蔑视</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/trump-team-rejects-market-fears-projecting-defiance-on-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统的高级经济官员驳斥了投资者对通货膨胀和衰退的恐惧，对全球关税席卷全球关税引发的市场动荡并没有道歉，并坚持坚持繁荣。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/trump-team-rejects-market-fears-projecting-defiance-on-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 20:07:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
